text.tspan: │ Pointer Array End │ = Header End + (2 × count) │
│ Cell Content Start │ stored in header at 5-6 │
│ Free Space Start │ = Pointer Array End │
│ Free Space End │ = Cell Content Start │
│ Payload Size │ varint │ Total payload bytes │
│ Row ID │ varint │ Primary key value │
│ Payload │ N bytes │ Actual row data │
Each pointer: offset to cell in content area
Sorted by key for binary search
Gap between pointer array and cell content
Cells contain: payload size, rowid (table only), payload, overflow ptr
